						il fato, e predestinatione, secondo Zenone Stoico. )	
					</marginalia_text>
					<person name="Zeno of Citium"/>
				</position>
			</language>
			<translation>
				Fate and predestination, according to Zeno the Stoic.
			</translation>
		</marginalia>
		<marginalia hand="Italian">
			<language ident="LA">
				<position place="intext" book_orientation="0">
					<marginalia_text>
						At Aristippus tant&ograve; securi&ugrave;s dormiuisset.
					</marginalia_text>
					<person name="Aristippus"/>
				</position>
			</language>
			<translation>
				But Aristippus had been soundly sleeping so much.
			</translation>
		</marginalia>
		<marginalia hand="Italian">
